 Afrobeat star, Davido graced the screens of Jimmy Kimmel Live!, and he came, performed, and delivered. Davido had initially announced he would appear on the American late-night talk show, created and hosted by Jimmy Kimmel. On the show, the award-winning singer performed his 2019 hit track, “Assurance“, off “A Good Time” album, and 2020 track “Jowo“, off “A Better Time” album. Watch the electrifying performance below: 